19:37.840 --> 19:39.600
Dia asyik sebut nama awak.

19:39.880 --> 19:41.810
Sebab itulah mereka telefon awak.

19:43.280 --> 19:43.840
Si dungu.

19:44.680 --> 19:45.210
Si dungu.

19:45.920 --> 19:47.480
Dia dah mabuk teruk.

19:48.920 --> 19:50.380
